---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About | Hugo's musing"
  description="About Hugo Sarrazin and the ideas behind Hugo's musing."
  canonicalPath="/about/"
>
  <article class="post-shell">
    <header class="post-header">
      <p class="eyebrow">About</p>
      <h1>About Hugo</h1>
      <p class="lede">
        A little context on the person behind this blog and the themes that
        shape the writing here.
      </p>
    </header>

    <div class="prose">
      <p>
        Hugo Sarrazin writes about AI, technology, learning, and the systems
        that shape how people and organizations grow. His career has spanned
        product and technology leadership at <a href="https://about.udemy.com/press-releases/udemy-appoints-hugo-sarrazin-as-chief-executive-officer/">Udemy</a>,
        UKG, and McKinsey, where he helped build McKinsey Digital Labs. This
        blog is a place to reflect on product strategy, workforce
        transformation, and the practical impact of AI on how we learn, work,
        and build.
      </p>
    </div>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
